title: Delia Smith's winter collection. Parts 1 & 2
brief_description: Twelve episodes filled with warm recipes for winter food by well-known culinary expert Delia Smith. Filmed from her home kitchen in Suffolk, Delia prepares a veritable feast of soups, starters, casseroles, seafood, roasts, poultry and desserts as well as winter baking. This program will undoubtedly get the mouth watering and the most reluctant cook back in the kitchen.
